  })();        Most of the snippet templating settings should be made in the MODX system settings, since they are used by the snippets and with ajax.    The xPOD object package and class name have to be selected    In the  itemTitleTpl  template chunk all column names of the xPDO object could be referenced by a placeholder with this name. Also all properties could be referenced with the property name, i.e. a property set by  [[+rememberqueryadd]]property_test  could be referenced with a placeholder  [[+test]] .
